Biography of Patrick Harshman
                Last update: June 6, 2017            







Career

                                                                                Patrick Harshman graduated from University of Florida and from University of California, Berkeley.                                                                                Patrick was Director of Product Line Management for Digital Systems.                                                                                 Patrick Harshman joined Harmonic in 1994. Patrick served as President of the Convergent Systems division and President of Broadband Access Networks Division for Harmonic.                                                

Patrick Harshman is currently

President, Chief Executive Officer, Director - Harmonic


